  "steps": [
    "Take gram flour in a bowl, add yogurt and whisk till there are no lumps. Add 2½ cups water and mix well.",
    "Heat 2 tablespoons ghee in a non-stick kadai, add cumin seeds and once they start to change colour, add black peppercorns, cinnamon and cloves, mix and sauté till fragrant.",
    "Add yogurt mixture, salt and sugar and mix well.",
    "Add 1 cup water, mix well and cook on low heat for 4-5 minutes.",
    "Add ginger and sprouted green gram, mix and cook for 8-10 minutes.",
    "To make the second tempering, heat remaining ghee in a small non-stick pan. Break red chillies and add to the pan. Add turmeric powder, red chilli powder and asafoetida, mix and sauté for a few seconds.",
    "Add this tempering to the yogurt mixture and mix. Add coriander leaves, mix and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl and serve hot with steamed rice."
